text: Yulia Blindyuk (born 11 December 1984) is a road cyclist from Russia. She represented her nation at the 2006 and 2008 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1984 births Category:Russian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
